{
  "texts": [
    "• NaturalProofs (Welleck et al, 2021).",
    "The focus of the NaturalProofs dataset is on mathematical propositions and proof-related tasks, exploring mathematical reasoning expressed in natural language.",
    "The problem content encompasses statements and proofs of theorems, mathematical definitions, inferences based on axioms, etc., sourced from real-world materials like compilations of mathematical proofs and textbooks.",
    "• SVAMP (Patel et al, 2021).",
    "In addressing elementary applied mathematical problems, models are observed to predominantly depend on shallow heuristics rather than engage in deep reasoning."
  ]
}